---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about Murat Karslioglu. Background, experience, and interests."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <h1
      class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text-primary)] sm:text-5xl"
    >
      About
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
      <p>
        I'm Murat. Husband, father of three, and someone who's been writing
        code since age 8. I grew up in a nerdy engineering family where my
        dad was convinced German was the language of engineering. So I spent
        my formative years studying every science subject in German, and now
        I have a language I never get a chance to speak. Thanks, dad.
      </p>
      <p>
        By day, I build storage infrastructure for GPU compute and AI
        workloads at a leading neocloud company. I've founded three startups,
        written two Kubernetes books (<em>Kubernetes in Production Best
        Practices</em>, Packt 2021 and <em>Kubernetes: A Complete DevOps
        Cookbook</em>, Packt 2020), hold a patent for modular storage
        interfaces, and spent over a decade working across the storage stack.
        Previously I led Global Field Architects at MinIO, and held
        engineering and product roles at DataCore/MayaData, HPE Storage, and
        DDN/Nexenta.
      </p>
      <p>
        Fun fact: I had a tech TV show during my university years. I was
        also deeply addicted to collecting IT certifications. Over 40 taken.
        That's a cured disease now, but the scars remain.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2
        class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text-primary)]"
      >
        When I'm Not Staring at Storage Metrics
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
        <p>
          Big time Queen fan. I have a dream to play guitar like Brian May,
          and I'm now making that dream come through with my kids. We're
          getting there. Slowly.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm a graphic art nerd and have been using Adobe's tools since before
          Photoshop was called Photoshop. Our house is known as "the Harry
          Potter house" around the neighborhood during Halloween season, which
          I take as the highest compliment.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm stubbornly against digital books. I still buy and read physical
          copies, about 30-35 a year. I'm also a history geek, especially
          Sumerian history and the Sumerian language itself. Understanding how
          civilizations rise and fall helps me see the bigger picture and the
          seasonal patterns that keep repeating in our observed time.
        </p>
        <p>
          Other interests: classic cars and classic people.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2
        class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text-primary)]"
      >
        What I Work On
      </h2>
      <ul class="mt-6 grid gap-3 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] sm:grid-cols-2">
        {
          [
            "Storage Systems & Architecture",
            "AI Infrastructure",
            "Cloud-Native & Kubernetes",
            "Distributed Systems",
            "Product Strategy & GTM",
            "Technical Writing & Patents",
          ].map((skill) => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)]" />
              {skill}
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/muratkarslioglu/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline"
      >
        Connect on LinkedIn &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] pt-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-tertiary)]">
        The views and opinions expressed on this site are my own and do not
        necessarily reflect the views, positions, or policies of my employer or
        any organization I am affiliated with. All content is provided for
        informational purposes only.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
